extends ./shared/layout

block content
  .container
    .jumbotron.text-center
      h1 Welcome to NoteApp!
      p.lead
        | NoteApp is your simple and intuitive platform for organizing your ideas, tasks, and inspirations. Whether you're a student, a professional, or just someone who loves staying organized, 
        | our app helps you create, edit, and manage your notes easily. With the ability to tag and filter notes, you can keep everything in order and accessible at all times.

  .container.mt-5
    h2 Why Choose NoteApp?
    p 
      | NoteApp provides an easy-to-use interface with powerful features like note categorization, tag-based filtering, and more! With a focus on simplicity and efficiency, NoteApp ensures you stay productive without distractions.

    .row.mt-4
      .col-md-4
        h3 Organize Notes
        p
          | Create, edit, and categorize notes effortlessly. Keep your ideas sorted and accessible whenever you need them.
        
      .col-md-4
        h3 Tag and Filter
        p
          | Use tags to organize your notes by topic or priority. Our filtering options help you quickly find what you're looking for.

      .col-md-4
        h3 Stay Productive
        p
          | NoteApp helps you stay on top of your tasks and ideas, so you can focus on what matters most. Keep your workflow smooth and efficient.

    .text-center.mt-5
      a.btn.btn-light.btn-lg(href='/notes') 
        | Create Your First Note
        i.fa-solid.fa-arrow-right.ms-2